title: Windows 7 Applications Unity view with VWware Fusion 5.png
description:
Just find out that Windows 7 applications are running more smooth and sleeker on Mac, supported by VMWare Fusion, than on a naked PC hardware.

Unity view feature in VMWare Fusion let you run Windows programs without seeing Windows, but rather like native Mac applications instead. Plus, Windows applications benefits from MacBook Pro advantage hardware, responsive keyboard, Magic Trackpad ...

I feel so thrilled that first time in history Microsoft "famous" Internet Explorer 8 is running in Mac. How amazing!

Read more: http://www.vmware.com/products/fusion/overview.html
